Title: Johnson Controls F61 NPT liquid flow -30c
Description: Made of brass, this Johnson Controls F61 series 1" NPT liquid flow switch is a single-pole, double-throw (SPDT) switch for use on fluid lines carrying water, ethylene glycol or other non-hazardous fluids. This switch can be wired to energise one device and de-energise another powered from the same source when fluid flow exceeds or drops below a set flow rate.
